sentences.english: The Hohxil Region of Qinghai Province is one of the region studied less in the world.

sentences.english: The First Dodrupchen had many famous disciples in Sichuan and Qinghai.

sentences.english: The remoteness of Qinghai Province has made it the site of many prison camps.

sentences.english: Which international sport events have been carried out around the Qinghai tourism resources?

sentences.english: Ice on the Qinghai plateau is retreating at the rate of seven per cent every year.
sentences.chinese: 青海高原上的冰川正以每年7%的速率退缩。

sentences.english: Temperature is one of main factors influencing grasshopper outbreak in the region around Qinghai Lake.
sentences.chinese: 在青海湖地区，气温是影响草地蝗虫发生的主要因素。

sentences.english: Nephrite deposits in Qinghai Province have occurred in contact belt between intermediate-acidic intrusive rocks and dolomite-marble.
sentences.chinese: 青海软玉矿床产于中酸性侵入岩与大理岩接触带中。

sentences.english: The distribution characteristics of tritium in natural water in the area of Qinghai Lake is presented.
sentences.chinese: 本文报道了青海湖地区天然水中氚的分布及其变化。

sentences.english: The main reason for corrosion of oil pipelines in Qinghai oil field has been studied.
sentences.chinese: 研究了青海油田集输管线腐蚀的主要原因。

sentences.english: The source of the Yellow River can be traced to the Bayankela Mountains of Qinghai Province.
sentences.chinese: 黄河的发源地在青海的巴颜喀拉山上。
